title: Elvis Presley - High Voltage (Birmingham 1976 revisited) - Audio
description:
This is the re-release of the classic title "Burning In Birmingham" which features Elvis&#039; concert in Birmingham, Alabama, on December 29th, 1976. This is supposed to be one of the late Elvis&#039; better shows and probably one of the finest after 1975. According to the label the source for this release has been a better tape so the sound quality could have been improved. While IMO this is not the case it&#039;s still a good release and a chance for those who missed the original Burning In Birmingham a few years ago.

Encoded using the lossless format flac so you can burn a CD-R from this.
